sfcurve

\(n \times n\)

R, C++
CRAN https://cran.r-project.org/package=sfcurve
GitHub https://github.com/jokergoo/sfcurve
https://jokergoo.github.io/sfcurve/
Zuguang Gu, Construction, Transformation and Structures of 2x2 Space-Filling Curves. arXiv 2024.

2x2

library(sfcurve)
p = sfc_2x2("I", "2222", rot = 270)
p
